      <p>B2B wholesale Shopify stores break when email treats every subscriber the same. The pressure point is account approvals, bulk ordering, and rep follow-up. A disciplined email marketing program must coordinate consent, lifecycle timing, product context, and margin-aware measurement — not blast more coupons.</p>
